Connectivity Mocdeling System (CMS) is developed by Claire B. Paris, at the Rosenstiel School of Marine and Atmospheric Science (RSMAS). All code is released under the GNU General Public License v3.0.
Code credit should be given by citing the publication: Paris CB, Helgers J, Van Sebille E, Srinivasan A (2013) Connectivity Modeling System (CMS): A multi-scale tool for the tracking of biotic and abiotic variability in the ocean, Environmental Modelling & Software, 42: 47-54 http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S136481521200312X
